Package pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1

Interface Map<K,V>

Type Parameters:
K - The type of keys maintained by this map.
V - The type of values associated with the keys.
All Known Implementing Classes:
MyMap
public interface Map<K,V>
The Map interface defines basic operations for a map data structure, which associates keys with values. Each key in the map is unique and is assigned exactly one value.
